    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood from any of various coniferous trees from which pitch or turpentine can be obtained and which yield very resinous wood.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
